# Deep links

## User-facing URLs (backend emails)

- Verify: `https://appfitech.com/verify-email?token={token}`
- Reset: `https://appfitech.com/reset-password?token={token}`

Do not use API paths (`/v1/app/user/...`) in email links.

## Native handling

- Route files: `app/verify-email/index.tsx`, `app/reset-password/index.tsx`
- Path rewriting: `app/+native-intent.tsx` + `utils/deep-link.ts`
- Server AASA must list **both** `/verify-email` and `/reset-password` ‚Äî see `docs/well-known/apple-app-site-association`

## Never use `Alert.alert` for in-app dialogs

Use `showAlert` from `@/contexts/AlertContext` (see `show-alert.mdc`).
